{"tid":1847983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳灣口岸健康申報情況","createTime":"2020-01-28T09:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T08:27:21.000Z","uid":258177,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ceeecd0dc80725a6dceb1a927fe5b9f955da0960","tid":1847983,"uid":258177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:16:00.000Z","msg":"因為屋企需要 上左大陸幾日 <br />\n頭先過完關留意到幾個情況：<br />\n1.冇清晰指示健康申報表係邊到可以拎，建議d form可以放係唔同位置 唔係淨係集中放係一角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 海關淨係睇睇有冇tick去過武漢嗰欄，form上面要寫證件number，但海關核對你身份證明文件<br />\n4. 量體溫求其抽幾個人出黎量<br />\n<br />\n總之安排都幾混亂下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做左野等於冇做野<br />\n<br />\n利申 冇接觸過有發燒感冒症狀既人<br />\n但會自我隔離一排 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都要保重身子"},{"pid":"4dc376f3c40ca7917c0eadb3878a208546b5f22a","tid":1847983,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:16:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">匿埋喺屋企出唔到街？<br />\n唔夠口罩唔敢出去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter 戰線永遠需要你！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">入去 <a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=75a72162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a> 撳 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">/task2</span></span> 拎任務</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\nTask 2 好缺人，大家快啲去幫手！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，撳幾個掣都做唔到？<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n1. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1221867978716844032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1221867978716844032&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=f4f2a312\" data-